name: fastPlotXORAttr
parameters: x AS UBYTE, y AS UBYTE, color AS UBYTE
doc:
SUB fastcall fastPlotXORAttr

Plots a point at (x, y) in OVER 1 mode (XOR) with color as ATTR
This routine is slightly faster than PLOT XOR 1 with ATTRs

name: fastPlotXOR
parameters: x AS UBYTE, y AS UBYTE
doc:
SUB fastcall fastPlotXOR

Plots a point at (x, y) in OVER 1 mode (XOR)
This routine is slightly faster than PLOT XOR 1
